Activity Tracker requirements
1) Allow activities to be input by user
    1a) Date
    1b) Location
    1c) Distance
    1d) Total Time
    1e) Pace (calculated)
    1e) Type
    1f) Estimated Calorie Burn
    1g) Shoe used

2) Show Summary Widgets
    2a) Current Week, Month, Year, Lifetime
        2a1) Total Time (hh:mm:ss)
        2a2) Total Distance (miles)
        2a3) Total Calorie Burn
        2a4) Number of Runs
        2a5) Number of Walks
    2b) Shoe Summary
        2b1) Number of activities
        2b2) Number of Runs
        2b3) Number of Walks
        2b4) Lifetime Miles

3) Shoe Management
    3a) Add New Shoe
        3a1) Shoe Manufacturer
        3a2) Shoe Model
        3a3) Shoe Nickname
    3b) Retire Shoe